## 2. 기존 Service, Controller, Entity 파일들

### 아직 구현되지 않음
현재 프로젝트에는 실제 구현 파일이 없으나, 다음 구조로 개발될 예정입니다.

#### Entity (domain 모듈에 위치)
**경로**: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/notification/`

**예상 Entity 클래스들** (Entity-Skill 기준):
- `NotificationEntity` — 푸시알림 데이터
- `NotificationSettingEntity` — 사용자별 알림 설정

**특징**:
- Catalog: `notification` (DB 카탈로그명)
- ID 전략: UUID (`@GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")`)
- 감사 필드: `createdAt`, `updatedAt` (LocalDateTime)

**예상 필드 예시**:
```kotlin
class NotificationEntity(
    @Id val id: String,
    val userId: String,
    val type: Int,           // 알림 타입 (Int로 저장)
    val title: String,
    val message: String,
    val isRead: Boolean = false,
    val actionUrl: String? = null,
    @CreatedDate var createdAt: LocalDateTime,
    @LastModifiedDate var updatedAt: LocalDateTime,
)
```

#### Repository (domain 모듈)
**경로**: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/notification/`

**예상 Repository 인터페이스**:
```kotlin
interface NotificationRepository : JpaRepository<NotificationEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): List<NotificationEntity>
    fun findByUserIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(userId: String): List<NotificationEntity>
    fun countByUserIdAndIsReadFalse(userId: String): Int
}

interface NotificationSettingRepository : JpaRepository<NotificationSettingEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): NotificationSettingEntity?
}
```

#### Service (notification 모듈)
**경로**: `notification/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/`

**예상 Service 클래스들**:
- `NotificationService` — 푸시알림 발송, 조회, 삭제 로직
- `NotificationSettingService` — 알림 설정 관리

**특징**:
- `@Transactional` 적용
- Repository 주입 (직접 DB 접근)
- 비즈니스 로직 집중

**예상 메서드**:
```kotlin
@Service
class NotificationService(
    private val notificationRepository: NotificationRepository,
) {
    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getNotifications(userId: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): List<NotificationEntity>

    @Transactional
    fun sendNotification(userId: String, title: String, message: String): NotificationEntity

    @Transactional
    fun markAsRead(notificationId: String): Boolean

    @Transactional
    fun deleteNotification(notificationId: String): Boolean

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getUnreadCount(userId: String): Int
}
```

#### gRPC Service (notification 모듈)
**경로**: `notification/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/`

**클래스명**: `NotificationGrpcService` (extends `NotificationServiceGrpc.NotificationServiceImplBase()`)

**예상 메서드들**:
```kotlin
@GrpcService
class NotificationGrpcService(
    private val notificationService: NotificationService,
) : NotificationServiceGrpc.NotificationServiceImplBase() {

    override fun getNotifications(
        request: GetNotificationsRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<GetNotificationsResponse>,
    )

    override fun sendNotification(
        request: SendNotificationRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<SendNotificationResponse>,
    )

    override fun markAsRead(
        request: MarkAsReadRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<MarkAsReadResponse>,
    )

    override fun deleteNotification(
        request: DeleteNotificationRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<DeleteNotificationResponse>,
    )

    override fun getUnreadCount(
        request: GetUnreadCountRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<GetUnreadCountResponse>,
    )
}
```

#### Service 테스트
**경로**: `notification/src/test/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/`

**클래스명**: `NotificationServiceTest`

**패턴** (Test-Skill 기준):
- `@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension::class)`
- `@Mock` + `@InjectMocks` 사용
- given-when-then 패턴
- 메서드: `should return notifications by userId`, `should throw when invalid`, 등

---

## 3. Protobuf에서 Notification 관련 .proto 파일

**경로**: `protobuf/src/main/proto/notification/notification.proto`

**파일 구조**:
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package notification;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.notification";

service NotificationService {
  rpc GetNotifications(GetNotificationsRequest) returns (GetNotificationsResponse);
  rpc SendNotification(SendNotificationRequest) returns (SendNotificationResponse);
  rpc MarkAsRead(MarkAsReadRequest) returns (MarkAsReadResponse);
  rpc DeleteNotification(DeleteNotificationRequest) returns (DeleteNotificationResponse);
  rpc GetUnreadCount(GetUnreadCountRequest) returns (GetUnreadCountResponse);
}

// Request/Response 메시지들
message GetNotificationsRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  int32 limit = 2;
  int32 offset = 3;
}

message GetNotificationsResponse {
  repeated Notification notifications = 1;
  int32 total_count = 2;
}

message Notification {
  string id = 1;
  string user_id = 2;
  string title = 3;
  string message = 4;
  int32 type = 5;
  bool is_read = 6;
  string action_url = 7;
  string created_at = 8;
}

message SendNotificationRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  string title = 2;
  string message = 3;
  int32 type = 4;
  optional string action_url = 5;
}

message SendNotificationResponse {
  Notification notification = 1;
}

message MarkAsReadRequest {
  string notification_id = 1;
}

message MarkAsReadResponse {
  bool success = 1;
}

message DeleteNotificationRequest {
  string notification_id = 1;
}

message DeleteNotificationResponse {
  bool success = 1;
}

message GetUnreadCountRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
}

message GetUnreadCountResponse {
  int32 count = 1;
}
```

**주요 특징**:
- 패키지명: `notification`
- 서비스명: `NotificationService`
- `java_multiple_files = true` (각 메시지가 별도 파일로 생성)
- snake_case 필드명 (Proto 컨벤션)
- `optional` 키워드로 선택 필드 명시

---

## 4. GraphQL 모듈에서 Notification 관련 파일

### GraphQL Schema
**경로**: `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/notification.graphqls`

```graphql
type Notification {
  id: ID!
  title: String!
  message: String!
  type: NotificationType!
  isRead: Boolean!
  actionUrl: String
  createdAt: String!
}

enum NotificationType {
  CALL_REQUEST
  MESSAGE
  PROMOTION
  FRIEND_REQUEST
  SYSTEM
}

input SendNotificationInput {
  title: String!
  message: String!
  type: NotificationType!
  actionUrl: String
}

extend type Query {
  notifications(limit: Int, offset: Int): [Notification!]!
  unreadCount: Int!
  notification(id: ID!): Notification
}

extend type Mutation {
  sendNotification(input: SendNotificationInput!): Notification!
  markAsRead(id: ID!): Boolean!
  deleteNotification(id: ID!): Boolean!
}
```

### GraphQL Controller
**경로**: `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/notification/`

**클래스명**: `NotificationController`

```kotlin
@Controller
class NotificationController(
    private val notificationService: NotificationService,
) {
    @QueryMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun notifications(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument limit: Int?,
        @Argument offset: Int?,
    ): List<NotificationResponse> {
        val response = notificationService.getNotifications(userId, limit ?: 20, offset ?: 0)
        return response.notificationsList.map { it.toResponse() }
    }

    @QueryMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun unreadCount(
        @UserId userId: String,
    ): Int {
        val response = notificationService.getUnreadCount(userId)
        return response.count
    }

    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun markAsRead(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument id: String,
    ): Boolean {
        val response = notificationService.markAsRead(userId, id)
        return response.success
    }

    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun deleteNotification(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument id: String,
    ): Boolean {
        val response = notificationService.deleteNotification(userId, id)
        return response.success
    }
}
```

### GraphQL Service (gRPC Client)
**경로**: `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/notification/`

**클래스명**: `NotificationService`

```kotlin
@Service
class NotificationService {
    @GrpcClient("notification-grpc")
    private lateinit var stub: NotificationServiceGrpc.NotificationServiceBlockingStub

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getNotifications(userId: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): GetNotificationsResponse {
        val request = GetNotificationsRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId(userId)
            .setLimit(limit)
            .setOffset(offset)
            .build()
        return try {
            stub.getNotifications(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.status.code.name, e.status.description)
        }
    }

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getUnreadCount(userId: String): GetUnreadCountResponse {
        val request = GetUnreadCountRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId(userId)
            .build()
        return try {
            stub.getUnreadCount(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.status.code.name, e.status.description)
        }
    }
}
```

