## 5. Domain 모듈에서 Notification 관련 Entity/Repository

### Entity 위치 및 구조
**경로**: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/notification/`

**Catalog**: `notification` (전용 DB 카탈로그)

**Entity 클래스 (상세)**:

#### NotificationEntity
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "notification", name = "notification")
class NotificationEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    // 비즈니스 필드
    val userId: String,
    val type: Int,           // Enum을 Int로 저장 (0=CALL, 1=MESSAGE, 2=PROMOTION, ...)
    val title: String,
    val message: String,
    var isRead: Boolean = false,
    val actionUrl: String? = null,

    // 감사 필드
    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

#### NotificationSettingEntity
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "notification", name = "notification_setting")
class NotificationSettingEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val userId: String,
    var allowCall: Boolean = true,
    var allowMessage: Boolean = true,
    var allowPromotion: Boolean = true,
    var allowFriend: Boolean = true,
    var allowSystem: Boolean = true,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

#### Enum 정의
```kotlin
enum class NotificationType(val value: Int) {
    CALL_REQUEST(0),
    MESSAGE(1),
    PROMOTION(2),
    FRIEND_REQUEST(3),
    SYSTEM(4);

    companion object {
        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }
    }
}
```

### Repository 위치 및 구조
**경로**: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/notification/`

#### NotificationRepository
```kotlin
interface NotificationRepository : JpaRepository<NotificationEntity, String> {
    // 기본 조회
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): List<NotificationEntity>

    // 시간순 조회
    fun findByUserIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(userId: String): List<NotificationEntity>

    // 페이지네이션
    fun findByUserIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(userId: String, pageable: Pageable): Page<NotificationEntity>

    // 미읽음 조회
    fun findByUserIdAndIsReadFalse(userId: String): List<NotificationEntity>

    // 미읽음 개수
    fun countByUserIdAndIsReadFalse(userId: String): Int

    // 타입별 조회
    fun findByUserIdAndType(userId: String, type: Int): List<NotificationEntity>

    // 복합 조건 (QueryDSL 필요시)
    fun findByComplexCondition(userId: String, type: Int?, isRead: Boolean?): List<NotificationEntity>
}

// QueryDSL Custom Repository
interface CustomNotificationRepository {
    fun findByComplexCondition(userId: String, type: Int?, isRead: Boolean?): List<NotificationEntity>
}

class CustomNotificationRepositoryImpl(
    private val queryFactory: JPAQueryFactory,
) : CustomNotificationRepository {
    override fun findByComplexCondition(userId: String, type: Int?, isRead: Boolean?): List<NotificationEntity> {
        val entity = QNotificationEntity.notificationEntity
        return queryFactory
            .selectFrom(entity)
            .where(
                entity.userId.eq(userId),
                type?.let { entity.type.eq(it) },
                isRead?.let { entity.isRead.eq(it) }
            )
            .orderBy(entity.createdAt.desc())
            .fetch()
    }
}
```

#### NotificationSettingRepository
```kotlin
interface NotificationSettingRepository : JpaRepository<NotificationSettingEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): NotificationSettingEntity?
}
```

