## 3. Protobuf에서 Notification 관련 .proto 파일

**경로**: `protobuf/src/main/proto/notification/notification.proto`

**파일 구조**:
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package notification;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.notification";

service NotificationService {
  rpc GetNotifications(GetNotificationsRequest) returns (GetNotificationsResponse);
  rpc SendNotification(SendNotificationRequest) returns (SendNotificationResponse);
  rpc MarkAsRead(MarkAsReadRequest) returns (MarkAsReadResponse);
  rpc DeleteNotification(DeleteNotificationRequest) returns (DeleteNotificationResponse);
  rpc GetUnreadCount(GetUnreadCountRequest) returns (GetUnreadCountResponse);
}

// Request/Response 메시지들
message GetNotificationsRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  int32 limit = 2;
  int32 offset = 3;
}

message GetNotificationsResponse {
  repeated Notification notifications = 1;
  int32 total_count = 2;
}

message Notification {
  string id = 1;
  string user_id = 2;
  string title = 3;
  string message = 4;
  int32 type = 5;
  bool is_read = 6;
  string action_url = 7;
  string created_at = 8;
}

message SendNotificationRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  string title = 2;
  string message = 3;
  int32 type = 4;
  optional string action_url = 5;
}

message SendNotificationResponse {
  Notification notification = 1;
}

message MarkAsReadRequest {
  string notification_id = 1;
}

message MarkAsReadResponse {
  bool success = 1;
}

message DeleteNotificationRequest {
  string notification_id = 1;
}

message DeleteNotificationResponse {
  bool success = 1;
}

message GetUnreadCountRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
}

message GetUnreadCountResponse {
  int32 count = 1;
}
```

**주요 특징**:
- 패키지명: `notification`
- 서비스명: `NotificationService`
- `java_multiple_files = true` (각 메시지가 별도 파일로 생성)
- snake_case 필드명 (Proto 컨벤션)
- `optional` 키워드로 선택 필드 명시

